</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-44_ pf-text-1"><em><strong><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/childcare-and-early-years-courses-training" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span></a></strong></em><strong>Data protection</strong> - In the digital age, protecting personal data is critical. A robust data protection policy ensures compliance with GDPR and safeguards the information of children, parents, and staff. This policy should include procedures for data handling, storage, and breaches.




</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-46_ pf-text-1"><em><strong><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/childcare-and-early-years-courses-training" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span></a></strong></em><strong>SEND Policy</strong> - Supporting children with special educational needs requires a dedicated policy outlining the nursery’s identification, assessment, and intervention approach. Regular staff training and resources are crucial to effectively supporting these children.





